# unified_receipt.Latest_receipt_info

**Object**

An object that contains information about the latest in-app subscription transaction.

## Declaration

```swift
object unified_receipt.Latest_receipt_info
```

## Objects

- **unified_receipt.Pending_renewal_info**: An array of elements that refers to open auto-renewable subscription renewals or ones that failed in the past.
